.012 \\pm0.147 d Myr^{-1},\n<alpha> = 0.013 \\pm 0.279 Myr^{-1}), in excellent agreement with HB\nevolutionary model predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Oct 2010 10:23:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
