ure missions using a P(D) formalism, and the Universe opacity to TeV photons\ndue to the CIB.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Oct 2010 13:33:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2011 07:16:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
